content: If anyone has made a study guide or cheat sheet yet, what did you put on it? For the MicroQuiz cheat sheets I always had a full double-sided page of stuff that I didn’t end up needing, and I didn’t have the things I did need. Does anyone have any advice?
subject: Final Exam Study Guide/Cheat Sheet

content:
I added a reference of which of {}, (), and [] make dicts, tuples, and lists, because I seem to forget often.

I also added how to add to each of those, how to remove from each, how to get the first item, how to copy by reference and by value.
